OL,3,CBoy, 15, becomes first person charged
OL,4,Cwith riot following nationwide disorder
OL,6,FThe Crown Prosecution Service said the
OL,7,Fboy, from Sunderland, is accused of
OL,8,Friot following disorder in his home
OL,9,Fcity on 2 August.
OL,11,FGale Gilchrist, chief Crown Prosecutor
OL,12,Ffor CPS North East, said: "Following a
OL,13,Freview of further evidence, the Crown
OL,14,FProsecution Service has today laid a
OL,15,Fcharge of riot in relation to a 15-
OL,16,Fyear-old boy, following disorder that
OL,17,Ftook place in Sunderland on August 2.
OL,19,F"This is the first such charge to be
OL,20,Fauthorised by the Crown Prosecution
OL,21,FService in the wake of recent unrest.
