OL,6,F"The boy, from Sunderland, will appear
OL,7,Fat South Tyneside Youth Court today
OL,8,F(August 15, 2024) where he will be
OL,9,Fasked to enter a plea.
OL,11,F"This defendant is one of a number of
OL,12,Findividuals who we expect will be
OL,13,Fcharged with riot, and as these are
OL,14,Flive proceedings we remind all
OL,15,Fconcerned that there should be no
OL,16,Freporting, commentary or sharing of
OL,17,Finformation online which could in any
OL,18,Fway prejudice these proceedings."
