OL,3,CBoy, 15, becomes first person charged
OL,4,Cwith riot following nationwide disorder
OL,6,FSix people have so far been jailed for
OL,7,Ftheir part in the disorder in
OL,8,FSunderland - all having pleaded guilty
OL,9,Fto violent disorder.
OL,11,FSeveral others have pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fviolent disorder and await sentencing.
OL,14,FAssistant Chief Constable Alastair
OL,15,FSimpson, of Northumbria Police, said:
OL,16,F"I hope this sends a really strong
OL,17,Fmessage that, no matter how old you
OL,18,Fare, if you took part in the recent
OL,19,Fappalling events in Sunderland, you
OL,20,Fwill face really serious charges.
