OL,6,F"Our investigations team are doing a
OL,7,Ffantastic job trawling through the
OL,8,Fhours and hours of footage and
OL,9,Fintelligence we have from that night.
OL,11,F"I would like to thank the public who
OL,12,Fhave continued to supply us with
OL,13,Fimages, video and information to help
OL,14,Fus build that evidential picture.
OL,16,F"The team have worked amazingly
OL,17,Fquickly, with our criminal justice
OL,18,Fpartners, to arrest those responsible
OL,19,Fand bring them before the courts."
